description:
Bobby shares a big TV announcement happening within the next couple weeks! Morgan texted Bobby last night about something he had to attend to urgently. He shares what he and everyone on the show is at risk of.  Bobby shares his experience being catfished and we find out another member of the show was convinced they were once talking to a celebrity online!!!
